## Part 11: Summary of New Data Structures

### Quality rank enum/constants

```typescript
const QUALITY_HIGH       = 1;
const QUALITY_MEDIUM_A   = 2;
const QUALITY_MEDIUM_B   = 3;
const QUALITY_MEDIUM_C   = 4;
const QUALITY_MEDIUM_D   = 5;
const QUALITY_LOW_A      = 6;  // same rank as TAIL_AP
const QUALITY_TAIL_AP    = 6;
const QUALITY_LOW_B      = 7;  // same rank as TAIL_BP
const QUALITY_TAIL_BP    = 7;
const QUALITY_NONE       = 99;
```

### Zone determination function

```typescript
function _currentZone(serial: number, today: number): 'A' | 'B' | 'C' | 'D' | null {
  var dayNum = serial - today + 1;  // today = day 1
  if (dayNum === 1) return 'A';
  if (dayNum <= 3) return 'B';
  if (dayNum <= 6) return 'C';
  if (dayNum <= 10) return 'D';
  return null;  // beyond display window
}
```

### Mask die lookup

```typescript
var MASK_DICE = {
  medium: { A: 20, B: 12, C: 10, D: 8 },
  low:    { A: 6,  B: 4 },
  tail:   { Ap: 6, Bp: 4 }
};
```

### Jitter level lookup

```typescript
// Returns number of traits affected: 0, 1, 2, or 3
var JITTER_LEVEL = {
  medium: { A: 0, B: 1, C: 2, D: 3 },
  low:    { A: 1, B: 3 },
  tail:   { Ap: 1, Bp: 3 }
};
```

